? In fluid dynamics, what is a Karman vortex street?
[A] A turbulent boundary layer that forms along flat surfaces at high speed
[B] A spiral flow pattern inside centrifugal pumps
[C] A shock wave pattern produced by supersonic aircraft
[D]* A repeating pattern of alternating vortices shed behind a bluff body in a flow
